label: Parent Record; Atlas and farmers' directory of Sibley County, Minnesota, 1914

metadata.label: Description
metadata.value: Atlas and farmers' directory of Sibley county, Minnesota, containing plats of all townships with owners names also maps of the state and United States, with an outline map of the county showing location of townships, villages, roads, schools, churches, railroads, streams, etc.
